title: Trouble with the Tigers
description:
Jen Ladan, David Pollack, and Desmond Howard discuss the unfamiliar start to the CFB season for the Clemson Tigers. Jack Coan also prepares to play his former team in Wisconsin and the crew breaks down expectations for Notre Dame vs Wisconsin.
